V(x) = 0
x\in(0,a)
V(x) = \infty
\psi(x,0) = \alpha x (a-x)
\alpha\in\mathbb R
\alpha=\frac{a^3}{6}
\psi(x,0)
\psi(x,0)=\sum_{n=1}^{\infty} C_n u_n(x)
u_n(x) = \sqrt{\frac{2}{a}}\sin\left(\frac{n\pi x}{a}\right)
n
C_n = 4\left(\frac{a}{n\pi}\right)^3\frac{a^3}{6}\sqrt{\frac{2}{a}}= \frac{2}{3}\frac{a^6}{n^3\pi^3}\sqrt{\frac{2}{a}}
C_n = 0
C_n =\int_0^a u_n^*(x)\psi(x,0) dx
= \frac{a^3}{6}\sqrt{\frac{2}{a}}\int_0^a\sin\left(\frac{n\pi x}{a}\right)x (a-x)dx
= \frac{a}{n\pi}\frac{a^3}{6}\sqrt{\frac{2}{a}} \int_0^a(2x-a)\cos\left(\frac{n\pi x}{a}\right)dx
=-2\left(\frac{a}{n\pi}\right)^2\frac{a^3}{6}\sqrt{\frac{2}{a}}\int_0^a\sin\left(\frac{n\pi x}{a}\right)dx
\psi(x,0)=\sum_{\text{odd n}} \frac{4}{3}\frac{a^5}{n^3\pi^3}\sin\left(\frac{n\pi x}{a}\right)
\psi(x,t) = \sum_{\text{odd n}} \frac{4}{3}\frac{a^5}{n^3\pi^3}\sin\left(\frac{n\pi x}{a}\right) e^{-iE_nt/\hbar}
\alpha=6/a^3
